page_description: Learn about performance and latency with Azure OpenAI
chunk_content: How to measure your throughputWe recommend measuring your overall throughput on a deployment with two measures:-	Calls per minute: The number of API inference calls you're making per minute. This can be measured in Azure-monitor using the Azure OpenAI Requests metric and splitting by the ModelDeploymentName-	Total Tokens per minute: The total number of tokens being processed per minute by your deployment. This includes prompt & generated tokens. This is often further split into measuring both for a deeper understanding of deployment performance. This can be measured in Azure-Monitor using the Processed Inference tokens metric. You can learn more about Monitoring the Azure OpenAI Service.
